rd%20of%20Soviet%20Communist%20rule.%0AThe%20willingness%20of%20the%20new%20Russian%20Archival%20Committee%20under%20Pikhoia%20to%0Acooperate%20in%20preparing%20this%20exhibit%20with%20the%20Library%20of%20Congress%20dramatizes%0Athe%20break%20that%20a%20newly%20democratic%20Russia%20is%20attempting%20to%20make%20with%20the%20entire%0ASoviet%20past.%20%20%0AThis%20exhibit%20illustrates%20both%20the%20domestic%20and%20the%20foreign%20policy%20of%20Soviet%0Arule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ibiblio.org%2Fexpo%2F1492.exhibit%2FIntro.html%22%3E1492%20Exhibit%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cb%3E1492%3A%20AN%20ONGOING%20VOYAGE%3C%2Fb%3E%20examines%20the%20first%20sustained%20contacts%20between%20American%20people%0Aand%20European%20explorers%2C%20conquerors%20and%20settlers%20from%201492%20to%201600.%20During%0Athis%20period%2C%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20Columbus's%20voyages%2C%20Africans%20also%20arrived%20in%20the%0Ahemisphere%2C%20usually%20as%20slaves.%20All%20of%20these%20encounters%2C%20some%20brutal%20and%0Atraumatic%2C%20others%20more%20gradual%2C%20irreversibly%20changed%20the%20way%20in%20which%20peoples%0Ain%20the%20Americas%20led%20their%20lives.%20The%20dramatic%20events%20following%201492%20set%20the%0Astage%20for%20numerous%20cultural%20interactions%20in%20the%20Americas%20which%20are%20still%20in%0Aprogress%20-%20a%20complex%20and%20ongoing%20voyage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ibiblio.org%2Fexpo%2Fdeadsea.scrolls.exhibit%2Fintro.html%22%3E%0ADead%20Sea%20Scrolls%20Exhibit%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cp%3E%0AThe%20exhibition%20%3Cb%3ESCROLLS%20FROM%20THE%20DEAD%20SEA%3A%20THE%20ANCIENT%20LIBRARY%20OF%20%0AQUMRAN%20AND%20MODERN%20SCHOLARSHIP%3C%2Fb%3E%0Abrings%20a%20selection%20from%20the%20scrolls%20which%20have%20been%20the%20subject%20of%20intense%0Apublic%20interest.%20%20Over%20the%20years%20questions%20have%20been%20raised%20about%0Athe%20scrolls'%20authenticity%2C%20about%20the%20people%20who%20hid%20them%20away%20the%0Athe%20period%20in%20which%20they%20lived%2C%20about%20the%20secrets%20the%20scrolls%0Amight%20reveal%2C%20and%20about%20the%20intentions%20of%20the%20scrolls'%20custodians%0Ain%20restricting%20access.%20%20The%20Library's%20exhibition%20describes%20the%0Ahistorical%20context%20of%20the%20scrolls%20and%20the%20Qumran%20community%20from%0Awhence%20they%20may%20have%20originated%3B%20it%20also%20relates%20the%20story%20of%0Atheir%20discovery%202%2C000%20years%20later.%20%20In%20addition%2C%20the%20exhibition%0Aencourages%20a%20better%20understanding%20of%20the%20challenges%20and%0Acomplexities%20connected%20with%20scroll%20research.%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ibiblio.org%2Fexpo%2Fpaleo.exhibit%2Fpaleo.html%22%3E%0APaleontology%20Exhibit%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cp%3E%0AThe%20Museum%20of%20Paleontology%2C%20from%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Berkeley%0Ahas%20created%20this%20nice%20pavilion%2C%20which%20shows%20%3Cb%3EAN%20EXHIBITION%20OF%20FOSSIL%20LIFE%3C%2Fb%3E.%0APaleontologist%20study%20past%20life%20by%20understanding%20both%20the%20biology%20and%20%0Aevolution%20of%20organisms%20and%20the%20geology%20of%20where%20the%20organisms%20are%20found.%0AThese%20two%20lines%20of%20evidence%20help%20us%20to%20recreate%20the%20diversity%20of%20past%20%0Alife.%20%20This%20work%20helps%20to%20clarify%20major%20issues%20about%20large%20and%20small%0Ascale%20geologic%20events%2C%20large%20and%20small%20scale%20extinction%20and%20origination%0Aof%20groups%20of%20animals%2C%20and%20in%20general%20clarify%20the%20progression%20of%20life%0Aon%20earth.%20%20This%20exhibit%20presents%20some%20of%20the%20diversity%20of%20life%20that%0Ahas%20existed%20in%20the%20past.%0A%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ibiblio.org%2Fexpo%2Fpalace.exhibit%2Fintro.html%22%3E%0ASpalato%20Exhibit%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cp%3E%0AThe%20exhibit%20%3Cb%3ETHE%20%22PALACE%22%20OF%20DIOCLETIAN%20AT%20SPLIT%3C%2Fb%3E%20describes%20a%0Aunique%20structure%20from%20the%20later%20roman%20empire.%20The%20city%20of%20Spalato%0Awas%20founded%20by%20the%20emperor%20Diocletian%3B%20he%20made%20it%20his%20own%0Adwelling-place%2C%20and%20built%20within%20it%20a%20court%20and%20a%20palace.%0AThe%20importance%20of%20Spalato%20resides%20both%20in%20its%20state%20of%0Apreservation%2C%20and%20in%20the%20dearth%20of%20comparable%20examples%20from%20the%0ARoman%20world.%20There%20are%20no%20coherent%20palace%20structures%20left%20in%0AItaly.%20Architecture%20and%20History%20are%20some%20keywords%20for%20this%20exhibit%20which%20%0Ashows%20more%20than%2080%20objects.%0A%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%0A%3Ch3%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%22EXPO%22%3E%20restaurant%3C%2Fh3%3E%0AThe%20%3Ci%3EEXPO%20%3C%2Fi%3E%20restaurant%20only%20serves%20real%20masterpieces%20of%20French%20cookery.%0AIt%20is%20owned%20by%20Andr%C3%A9%20L.%20Cointreau%2C%20descendant%20of%0Atwo%20of%20France's%20most%20venerable%20families%2C%20the%20Cointreaus%20and%20the%0AR%C3%A9my-Martins.%20You%20can%20join%20him%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ibiblio.org%2Fexpo%2Frestaurant%2Frestaurant.html%22%3E%3Cb%3Ea%20table%20for%20six%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%0A%0A%3Ch3%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%22EXPO%22%3E%20post%20office%3C%2Fh3%3E%0AThe%20post%20office%20handles%20all%20incoming%20mail%20for%20the%20%3Ci%3EEXPO%20%3C%2Fi%3Efrom%20all%20over%20the%20world.%0AYou%20should%20pay%20a%20visit%20to%20the%20%3Ci%3EEXPO%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ibiblio.org%2Fexpo%2Fexpo%2Fpostoffice.html%22%3E%3Cb%3EPost%20Office%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20whenever%0Ayou%20send%20mail%20to%20the%20%3Ci%3EEXPO%3C%2Fi%3E.%0A%0A%3Ch3%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%22EXPO%22%3E%20overview%3C%2Fh3%3E%0AIf%20you%20have%20visited%20%3Ci%3EEXPO%20%3C%2Fi%3E%20before%20and%20know%20exactly%20which%20item%20%0Ayou%20wish%20to%20examine%2C%20you%20can%20use%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ibiblio.org%2Fexpo%2Fexpo%2Foverview.html%22%3E%0AOverview%20of%20Objects%20and%20Topics%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20shows%20an%20outline%20of%20the%20various%0Aexhibits%20and%20offers%20direct%20access%20to%20all%20objects%0Ain%20the%20%3Ci%3EEXPO%20%3C%2Fi%3Eexhibits.%20%0A%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%22EXPO%22%3E%20catalogs%3C%2Fh3%3E%0AThe%20catalogs%20from%20the%20exhibits%20are%20on%20sale%20at%20the%20%3Ci%3EEXPO%20%3C%2Fi%3E%0A%3Ca%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ibiblio.org%2Fexpo%2Fexpo%2Fbookstore.html%22%3E%3Cb%3EBook%20Store%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%0AThe%20Ticket%20Office%20does%20offer%20you%20a%20free%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ibiblio.org%2Fexpo%2Fexpo%2Fabout.html%22%3Eleaflet%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%0Athe%20Library%20of%20Congress.%0AFeel%20free%20to%20take%20one%20because%20the%20supply%20is%20unlimited.%0A%0A%3Ch3%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%22EXPO%22%3E%20organization%3C%2Fh3%3E%0AThe%20%3Ci%3EEXPO%20%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20organized%20by%20%3Ci%3EFrans%20van%20Hoesel%3C%2Fi%3E.%20If%20you%0Awant%20to%20build%20another%20pavilion%20on%20the%20%3Ci%3EEXPO%20%3C%2Fi%3Eterrain%2C%20please%20contact%0Ahim%20directly%20via%20the%20%3Ci%3EEXPO%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ibiblio.org%2Fexpo%2Fexpo%2Fpostoffice.html%22%3E%3Cb%3EPost%20Office%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%0ARemember%20that%20four%20of%20the%20six%20exhibits%20were%20built%20from%20text%20and%20images%20that%20are%0Aavailable%20from%20the%20Library%20of%20Congress%20and%20they%20deserve%20all%20the%20credits%20for%20it.%0AThe%20Library%20of%20Congress%20can%0Abe%20reached%20at%20%3Ci%3Elcweb%40loc.gov%3C%2Fi%3E%20The%20original%20data%20is%20available%0Avia%20anonymous%20ftp%20from%20%3Ci%3Eftp.loc.gov.%3C%2Fi%3E%20The%201942%20exhibit%20and%20the%20Dead%0ASea%20scrolls%20exhibit%20were%20hypertexted%20by%20%3Ci%3EJeff%20Barry%20(barry%40scholar.lib.utk.edu)%3C%2Fi%3E.%0AThe%20paleontology%20exhibit%20was%20created%20by%20%3Ci%3ERobert%20Guralnick%20(robg%40fossil.Berkeley.edu)%3C%2Fi%3E.%0AThe%20original%20data%20for%20the%20Spalato%20exhibit%20was%20provided%20by%0A%3Ci%3EMichael%20Greenhalgh%20(gremarth%40fac.anu.edu.au)%3C%2Fi%3E.%0A%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%22EXPO%22%3E%20bulletin%20board%3C%2Fh3%3E%0AAll%20over%20the%20%3Ci%3EEXPO%20%3C%2Fi%3Eterrain%20you%20will%20find%20the%20%3Ci%3EEXPO%20%3C%2Fi%3E%20%0A%3Ca%20href%3D%22http%3A%2Fwww.ibiblio.org%2Fexpo%2Fexpo%2Fbulletin.html%22%3E%3Cb%3EBulletin%20Board%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%0Awhich%20you%20can%20use%20to%20make%20comments%20about%20the%0Aexhibit.%20This%20is%20very%20much%20appreciated.%20The%20bulletin%20board%20also%0Acontains%20up%20to%20date%20info%20from%20the%20%3Ci%3EEXPO%20%3C%2Fi%3Eorganization.%0A%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cimg%20alt%3D%22EXPO%22%3E%20%20wishes%20to%20thank%20%3Ci%3E%0APaul%20Jones%2C%20Jonathan%20Magid%20and%20Dykki%20Settle%20(dykki_settle%40unc.edu)%20%0A%3C%2Fi%3E%20who%20are%20serving%20the%20%3Ci%3EEXPO%20%3C%2Fi%3E%20and%20the%20exhibits%0Afrom%20their%20Web%20server%20for%20public%20access.%20We%20also%0Athank%20%3Ci%3EK.D.Ellis%20%3C%2Fi%3E%20for%20all%20the%20help%20we%20got%0Aand%20the%20Library%20of%20Congress%20for%20putting%20the%20original%20data%20online.%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%0A%3Cimg%20alt%3D%22%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%22____________________________________________________%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cb%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%22EXPO%22%3E%20text%20and%20images%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20are%20for%20the%20personal%20use%20of%20students%2C%20scholars%2C%20and%20the%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20public.%20%20Any%20commercial%20use%20or%20publication%20of%20them%20is%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20strictly%20prohibited.%0A%3C%2Fb%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20align%3D%22top%22%20alt%3D%22____________________________________________________%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2Fhtml%3E"
